B.U9=new A.lB(B.N,"Users did not struggle with the complexity of the task itself \u2014 they struggled with not knowing where they were in the process. Every significant usability failure we observed mapped back to a missing or ambiguous progress signal.","Key insight",B.HZ,B.nm,null)
